  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 11th level, as long as the gunslinger has at least 1 grit point, she can reload a single barrel of a one-handed or two-handed firearm as a swift action once per round. If she has the @Compendium[pf1.feats.11ClnanF4PdEPd9g]{Rapid Reload} feat or is using an alchemical cartridge (or both), she can reload a single barrel of the weapon as a free action each round instead. Furthermore, using this deed does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p>"
    },
